    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >古老预言、神启异象与皇家诏令 共同交织 出这段离奇的史诗。但真相仍笼罩在重重迷雾之中…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333880/extras/e05eafacd139a291733e478ede1c7300.poster.avif?t=1758886168\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333880/extras/e05eafacd139a291733e478ede1c7300.webm?t=1758886168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>皇室庆典突生变故</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正值雷姆利亚贵族奢靡节庆之际，一桩谋杀案点燃了一场可追溯至1910年的复杂阴谋。重返案发现场，揭开真相面纱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>虔信者之忠</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着科技日渐式微，灵性信仰蓬勃发展。魅力非凡的灵导师借神谕之名崛起，聚拢起无数忠诚信徒。然而，即便身居高位者亦非完人，未必能恪守道德。在这样的统治下，凡有过失之人皆将面临严酷惩戒。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>血染圣坛</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >道德准则各执一词，终将引发权力纷争。建立在谎言之上的同盟终将崩塌，权力失衡席卷而来。最终，唯有一人能够胜出，统御众生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333880/extras/4cf1136f08aef0fdfebdffa1a05e2549.poster.avif?t=1758886168\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333880/extras/4cf1136f08aef0fdfebdffa1a05e2549.webm?t=1758886168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>解锁五大全新篇章</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在横跨1910至1950年的五个全新篇章中，探索围绕欺诈、财富与权力展开的主题。 你将穿梭于纸醉金迷的宴会、古老神殿与危机四伏的仪式，展开寻求真相之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>破译预言</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着阴谋逐步浮出水面，你将面临解码神秘讯息的挑战，并拼凑出这场谜团的全貌——直到最终令人震惊的真相现身。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333880/extras/3aa0e00b60ebc7dfc20c1966fc824f26.poster.avif?t=1758886168\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333880/extras/3aa0e00b60ebc7dfc20c1966fc824f26.webm?t=1758886168\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
